(53047, 96742, 0, 1, 'LOVE (Englisg Ver.)', '', '2012-08-24 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 4, 'heads up high\r\ntears dry, tears dry\r\nnothing can quite fix my mind\r\n\r\ndeep inside\r\ndreams rack, dreams rack\r\nlaughter seems to be the price\r\n\r\nheart crumbles tight\r\nyou get high\r\nbut the blurring triggers sadder fights\r\n\r\nuntil we cry\r\nuntil we die\r\ndon’t ask why, this is life and\r\nyou’ll never realize\r\n\r\nlove, I can’t bear to look\r\nloosen up the strings and I turn\r\nbut the memories they choke\r\nand my pride, it burns\r\n\r\nlove lingers to hell\r\nshattered, painfully ill\r\nwonder why you still\r\n\r\ntalking to me, joke with me, laugh at me\r\n(but) you’re not here\r\n\r\nwho says, love conquers all oh\r\nwho says, love conquers a', '', 271, '', '方陽', '徐小斯', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-08-24 15:32:41', '2015-03-12 13:55:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
